{"id":370455,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":10}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"124","ytitle":"","mtitle":"汽车兵连","ftitle":"","authors":["沙鸥"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>王琦</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>沙鸥诗　王琦画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆卡车跟着一辆卡车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如长龙在红色云中奔腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车一停，铁锹挥舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄色泥土垫高了坝身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看坝上千条幅印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又压上千条轮印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有虚掷一秒钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你该感到如何振奋!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是降伏洪水的接力赛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺金牌的只有我们时代的人!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"58·6·7北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\06\\586a020401.JPG\">"}]}